726, 200.8739, 201.7436, 207.879, 211.5444, 211.4584, 211.9452, 211.1033, 212.9302, 212.8039, 214.3975, 214.9237, 212.6222, 210.5621, 211.1551, 209.8644, 209.6209, 210.0276, 208.7966, 209.9581, 211.9046, 212.8661, 212.0577, 212.9951, 213.392, 213.5572, 214.5928, 215.7819, 216.7902, 217.5042, 217.6204, 216.6781, 217.7548, 220.4154, 219.8831, 219.4461, 218.7088, 220.4129, 220.6146, 220.0532, 220.7713, 222.6904, 222.5298, 224.5028, 226.0867, 228.7512, 227.684, 226.8984, 231.1223, 234.2106, 236.6994, 233.9324, 232.3444, 232.7849, 231.8515, 235.0311, 234.2084, 234.6515, 232.1635, 233.126, 232.5248, 232.5974, 231.3544, 230.6548, 234.2549, 237.0825, 236.1114, 233.5565, 233.8979, 236.7175, 237.129, 236.9957, 237.6838, 234.9912, 235.8429, 239.0049, 239.4903, 238.4492, 241.5335, 241.2972, 242.444, 243.065, 244.686, 237.1091, 234.2795, 235.5398, 234.7511, 234.3338, 236.1613, 236.0455, 236.6447, 238.066, 237.6551, 237.6907, 239.2729, 239.8026, 240.3072, 241.0019, 243.7333, 244.1469, 245.4038, 245.0527, 244.6845, 246.7354, 246.5499, 244.4808, 246.4456, 244.5029, 246.9882, 247.4717, 248.1635, 249.8155, 248.5227, 246.7701, 246.3671, 246.6825, 247.8543, 248.9686, 249.6571, 251.4133, 250.5656, 253.7566, 255.0366, 257.2224, 252.2117, 255.835, 254.2906, 255.2584, 254.5033, 253.5769, 253.0512, 250.8012, 249.5933, 249.5964, 247.7164, 249.2616, 250.7045, 250.7559, 252.5152, 253.2979, 251.2346, 250.2996, 246.5199, 246.2452, 245.3286, 246.5415, 246.0342, 245.6867, 248.2094, 247.2903, 247.7905, 246.3913, 246.4803, 245.431, 243.7067, 242.7185, 241.8581], "summary_html": "<h1>PLS 预测因子收益加权多因子模型（商品期货复现）</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>复现研报「alpha 是否可以被预测：基于 PLS 模型」的因子收益预测加权思路，移植到商品期货。先将日频行情按月末重采样，构建一组横截面商品因子（多窗口动量 mom12/6/3、短期反转、低波、长期动量、carry/carry 变化、基差、持仓量变化）；每个因子做横截面 rank 转连续多空信号，并计算其月度多空组合收益（因子收益序列）。对每条因子收益序列再提取 7 个因果择时指标（趋势均值、信噪比、相对长期波动的水平/动量/波动、拥挤度、市场状态），用滚动 60 个月的 PLS1（NIPALS 闭式回归，确定性可复现）预测下月因子收益。每月将各因子的 PLS 预测收益去均值、地板截断为 0、归一化作为因子权重，加权合成因子信号得到综合信号；横截面 rank 转方向后，按 0.15 年化波动率目标缩放（杠杆上限 2.0）成月度仓位，再前向填充到日频。属于截面多空、因子动态加权策略，每月（约 21 个交易日）再平衡。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.53</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>6.2%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-4.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3434</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.66</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>2.68</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.62 / 1.72</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.76</td><td>1.81</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.27</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.11</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.03</span></td><td>1.16</td><td>0.53</td><td>1.9</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.17</span></td><td>1.33</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>high</code></td><td>最高价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>low</code></td><td>最低价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3436</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>73.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>47.3</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>PLS_W</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>PLS rolling window (months)</td></tr><tr><td><code>N_PLS_COMPONENTS</code></td><td><code>1</code></td><td>PLS1</td></tr><tr><td><code>TARGET_VOL</code></td><td><code>0.15</code></td><td>annualized vol target</td></tr><tr><td><code>HISTORY_START</code></td><td><code>&quot;2010-01-01&quot;</code></td><td>lower bound only (no upper bound) for warm-up</td></tr><tr><td><code>B</code></td><td><code>Rstar @ Q</code></td><td>coefficients in centered/scaled space</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9087</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 2.22s</li>\n</ul>"}